{
  "stem": "7069.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Like, for instance, on Friday night at school, it says, well, on Monday morning-- over the speaker system-- a grades so-and-so-- it's always the younger grades-- we will have a bus for you ready on Monday morning.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we will show you what a bunch of Jews really look like.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You see, by that time, everybody had heard the propaganda about Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And in the classrooms, by the way, were bad pictures about Jews and compared with the Aryan master race pictures and on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So kids were already brainwashed negativity about Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "If they have never had met any Jewish people, person-to-person, now they get the education of what Jews are like.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And steadily repeated, of course it sinks in eventually.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And so now-- and these buses-- now we will show you what a bunch of Jews really look like.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And so they go onto the buses now, and are being loaded up in front of people like that, a motley-looking group, most of them like this doctor, the professor that I am talking about.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I was a handy fellow with my work, with my hands, as I say, building furniture.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I was used to carrying lumber, carrying furniture, besides my drawing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And so this, this physically work didn't-- I was, you know-- so it didn't make any difference to me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But there were some old guys that had never had the shovel in their hands.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And even a simple thing as a shovel and a pick axe, you have to know how to handle that, too, particularly when it was there like quote, unquote, 'professionally.'",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyways, so these kids now are standing in front of the bus and looking at this motley-looking group.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
